{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Look behind the scenes into how system applications enhance their Touch Bar content with more than the basic controls. Learn about NSScrubber, customizing the text bar, candidate list item, event handling, layout, animations, and more. Leverage the full power of the Touch Bar to take your Mac app to the next level."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-222-advanced-touch-bar"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Related-Sessions","level":2,"text":"Related Sessions"},{"type":"links","items":["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-207-Whats-New-in-Cocoa","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-211-Touch-Bar-Fundamentals"],"style":"list"}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-222-Advanced-Touch-Bar"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC17","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode","title":"Advanced Touch Bar"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2017\/222\/"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-207-Whats-New-in-Cocoa":{"type":"topic","kind":"article","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Join us for this annual session to learn about enhancements in Cocoa. Catch up on the latest APIs for Touch Bar, performance improvements like copy-on-write collections, new features such as document sharing, Swift improvements for key paths and archiving, and many other refinements to AppKit and Foundation APIs.  Get an overview of many topics and a guide to important related sessions throughout the week."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-207-Whats-New-in-Cocoa","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-207-whats-new-in-cocoa","role":"sampleCode","title":"What’s New in Cocoa"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17-211-Touch-Bar-Fundamentals":{"role":"sampleCode","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17-211-touch-bar-fundamentals","title":"Touch Bar Fundamentals","abstract":[{"text":"Touch Bar replaces the function keys that have long occupied the top of your keyboard with a versatile MultiTouch input device that features a Retina display. AppKit provides powerful APIs to let you easily leverage the power of Touch Bar in your applications. Learn how to use Touch Bar in your application to add context sensitive commands and flexible content to your user experience. This session will cover the basic concepts, design considerations, standard controls, IB support, and API that you will need to get started using Touch Bar.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-211-Touch-Bar-Fundamentals","type":"topic"},"WWDC17-Icon.png":{"alt":null,"type":"image","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17-Icon.png"}],"identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png"},"WWDC17.jpeg":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17.jpeg"}],"identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg","alt":null,"type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC17":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDC17-Icon.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"WWDC17.jpeg"}],"type":"topic","kind":"article","role":"collectionGroup","title":"WWDC17","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc17","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 9, Swift 4.0, iOS 11, macOS 10.13 (High Sierra), tvOS 11, watchOS 4."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Core NFC"},{"type":"text","text":" and more."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC17"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Learn More…","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"Learn More…","url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"},"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2017/222/":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2017\/222\/","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2017\/222\/","type":"download"}}}